fields.name: Country
fields.description: Country is used for areas included (or previously included) in ISO 3166-1, e.g. United States.

fields.name: City
fields.description: City is used for settlements of any size, including towns and villages.

fields.name: Island
fields.description: Island is used for islands and atolls which don't form subdivisions of their own, e.g. Skye. These are not considered when displaying the parent areas for a given area.
